<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="icon" href="/img/oauth2.png" type="image/png">

  <link href="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" id="bootstrap-css">
  <script src="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  <script src="//code.jquery.com/jquery-1.11.1.min.js"></script>

  <style>
    body{font-family:Lato,sans-serif}.main-head{height:150px;background:#fff}.main{padding:0 10px}.sidenav{height:100%;background-color:#000;overflow-x:hidden;padding-top:20px}.login-main-text{margin-top:20%;padding:60px;color:#fff}.login-main-text h2{font-weight:300}.btn-black{background-color:#000!important;color:#fff}@media screen and (max-height:450px){.sidenav{padding-top:15px}}@media screen and (max-width:680px){.sidenav{height:200px}.login-main-text{margin-top:20px}.login-form{margin-top:10%}.register-form{margin-top:10%}}@media screen and (min-width:680px){.main{padding-top:15px;margin-left:40%}.sidenav{width:40%;position:fixed;z-index:1;top:0;left:0}.login-form{margin-top:30%;padding:60px 0}.register-form{margin-top:20%}}
    pre {
      color: #e83e8c;
      word-break: break-word;
      background: #dedede;
      padding: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="sidenav">
  <div class="login-main-text">
    <h2>Login Page</h2>
    <p>El login aquí se hace en el servidor autorizador, para luego continuar con el pedido de autorización que inició el cliente web:.</p>
    <pre><%= JSON.stringify(state, null, 2) %></pre>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="main">
  <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
    <div class="login-form">
      <form action="/login?state=<%= state.state %>" method="post">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Username</label>
          <input type="text" name="username" class="form-control" placeholder="Username">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Password</label>
          <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control" placeholder="Password">
        </div>
        <% if (flash.error) { %>
        <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
          <%= flash.error.join(', ') %>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-black">Login</button>
        <!-- <button type="submit" class="btn btn-secondary">Register</button> -->
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
